FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about Bunny Social
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Bunny Social is a unique social media platform designed exclusively for rabbit owners to connect, share, and celebrate their furry friends.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I create an account for my rabbit?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply hop over to our sign-up page, enter your rabbit's name, upload a cute photo, and create a password. Your bunny's profile will be ready in no time!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I follow other rabbits on Bunny Social?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! You can follow other rabbits, like their posts, and even arrange playdates through our 'Hoppy Hour' feature.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is Bunny Social safe for my rabbit's information?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we take your rabbit's privacy seriously. Our carrot-grade security ensures that your bunny's personal information is always protected.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What special features does Bunny Social offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Bunny Social offers unique features like 'Ear of the Day' photo contests, 'Burrow Chats' for private messaging, and 'Veggie Sharing' to exchange healthy treat recipes for your furry friends.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How do I create a profile for my rabbit?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Creating a profile for your furry friend is easy! Simply click 'Sign Up,' enter your rabbit's name, breed, and favorite vegetable. Don't forget to upload an adorable profile picture!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can rabbits from different countries interact?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! BunnyBook is a global community. Your rabbit can make friends and share carrot recipes with bunnies from all around the world. We even have an auto-translate feature for international communication!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of content can I share on BunnyBook?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: BunnyBook welcomes all rabbit-friendly content! Share photos, videos, hop-along stories, and even arrange playdates. Just remember to keep it family-friendly – no predator talk allowed!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is there a mobile app for BunnyBook?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes! Our mobile app is available for both iOS and Android. Now your rabbit can update their status and check their feed from anywhere – the hutch, the garden, or even during vet visits!
